-- Swiss Finance Department’s Zurbruegg May Join SNB, NZZ Reports
-- B y   C a r o l y n   B a n d e l
-- 2012-01-15T08:49:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-15/swiss-finance-department-s-zurbruegg-may-join-snb-nzz-reports.html
Fritz Zurbruegg, head of the Swiss
Federal Financial Administration, is a favorite among possible
candidates for a place on the directorate of the country’s
 central bank , Neue Zuercher Zeitung reported, without saying how
it obtained the information.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Carolyn Bandel in Zurich at 
 cbandel@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Frank Connelly at   fconnelly@bloomberg.net  